name: Time Branches
description: (1000x1000, 30fps, 960 frames, 32s) This video was made by capturing a time-lapse of the sky for 254 frames every 16s and then using those frames to create this video using Processing. In each frame, some part of every frame from the original time-lapse is visible. Due to 40mb limit, high-quality video: https://tinyurl.com/buhkz8h2. Made by Alex Radomski (https://alexradomski.com), Twitter: @radomski_alex
